attributes = objects.Attributes(attributes=[primitives.Enumeration(enums.
    CryptographicAlgorithm, value=enums.CryptographicAlgorithm.AES, tag=
    enums.Tags.CRYPTOGRAPHIC_ALGORITHM)], tag=enums.Tags.COMMON_ATTRIBUTES)
value = objects.convert_attributes_to_template_attribute(attributes)
self.assertIsInstance(value, objects.TemplateAttribute)
self.assertEqual(value.tag, enums.Tags.COMMON_TEMPLATE_ATTRIBUTE)
self.assertIsInstance(value.attributes, list)
self.assertEqual(1, len(value.attributes))
self.assertIsInstance(value.attributes[0], objects.Attribute)
self.assertEqual('Cryptographic Algorithm', value.attributes[0].
    attribute_name.value)
self.assertEqual(primitives.Enumeration(enums.CryptographicAlgorithm, value
    =enums.CryptographicAlgorithm.AES, tag=enums.Tags.ATTRIBUTE_VALUE),
    value.attributes[0].attribute_value)
